title: Georgia O'Keeffe Yellow Hickory Leaves with Daisy Mug
description:
Mug developed from Georgia O’Keeffe’s Yellow Hickory Leaves with Daisy, 1928, from the Art Institute of Chicago’s collection.

Waking up in the morning is a lot easier with a good cup of coffee, and our mug featuring a detail from Georgia O'Keeffe's painting Yellow Hickory Leaves with Daisy, 1928.  A winning combination: durable, practical, and best of all, beautiful.

  • Size: 11oz.
  • Dimensions: 3.2 x 3.75 in.
  • Material: Ceramic
  • Dishwasher and microwave safe.
